subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jimmie Johnson also gave team owner Rick Hendrick his 10th Cup championship, including four with Jeff Gordon and one with Terry Labonte. No team has won as many titles.
